    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>19 October 1939</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 352</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">


<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-8ad32361-e71c-4a7e-afed-e46ef5241bcd'>
            
<p class="">63.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-f9911ff6-3723-437f-9d71-4af7acc5a1b7">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-f9911ff6-3723-437f-9d71-4af7acc5a1b7">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-f9911ff6-3723-437f-9d71-4af7acc5a1b7">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-f9911ff6-3723-437f-9d71-4af7acc5a1b7">
                Mr. Rhys Davies
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f9911ff6-3723-437f-9d71-4af7acc5a1b7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-10-19/debates/46a90bb0-097c-44af-8352-6d3109fdf97b/Personnel#contribution-f9911ff6-3723-437f-9d71-4af7acc5a1b7">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Home Secretary whether he has now been able to satisfy himself that persons following other occupations have been appointed to air-raid precautions and other civil defence posts and thereby drawing two incomes at the same time; and whether he intends taking any action to abolish this practice?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f9911ff6-3723-437f-9d71-4af7acc5a1b7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-10-19/debates/46a90bb0-097c-44af-8352-6d3109fdf97b/Personnel#contribution-f9911ff6-3723-437f-9d71-4af7acc5a1b7">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-678839bc-adcc-4bb3-868e-91c608a1b916">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-678839bc-adcc-4bb3-868e-91c608a1b916">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-678839bc-adcc-4bb3-868e-91c608a1b916">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-678839bc-adcc-4bb3-868e-91c608a1b916">
                Sir J. Anderson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-678839bc-adcc-4bb3-868e-91c608a1b916" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-10-19/debates/46a90bb0-097c-44af-8352-6d3109fdf97b/Personnel#contribution-678839bc-adcc-4bb3-868e-91c608a1b916">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">As I stated in reply to the hon. Member's question on 5th October, persons are not ineligible for whole-time paid service in the air-raid precautions service merely because they are in receipt of an income from other sources, but they must be in a position to give whole-time service at such times and for such hours of duty as are required of them and to take the necessary training for their service. Inquiries into the cases which the hon. Member has brought to my notice are being made locally in order to make sure that these conditions are being observed, and as soon as they are completed I will communicate with him.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-678839bc-adcc-4bb3-868e-91c608a1b916" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-10-19/debates/46a90bb0-097c-44af-8352-6d3109fdf97b/Personnel#contribution-678839bc-adcc-4bb3-868e-91c608a1b916">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-f4cd6c48-99ef-46a0-b83b-3e02cb9cff17">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-f4cd6c48-99ef-46a0-b83b-3e02cb9cff17">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-f4cd6c48-99ef-46a0-b83b-3e02cb9cff17">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-f4cd6c48-99ef-46a0-b83b-3e02cb9cff17">
                Mr. Davies
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f4cd6c48-99ef-46a0-b83b-3e02cb9cff17" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-10-19/debates/46a90bb0-097c-44af-8352-6d3109fdf97b/Personnel#contribution-f4cd6c48-99ef-46a0-b83b-3e02cb9cff17">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is the right hon. Gentleman satisfied that a person employed during the day and earning an income in respect of that employment is really available for the whole of the night for this A.R.P. work? How is it that the right hon. Gentleman is accepting that as a matter of course?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f4cd6c48-99ef-46a0-b83b-3e02cb9cff17" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-10-19/debates/46a90bb0-097c-44af-8352-6d3109fdf97b/Personnel#contribution-f4cd6c48-99ef-46a0-b83b-3e02cb9cff17">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-64d573b6-6104-4af6-b8a8-6dc3d226ba99">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-64d573b6-6104-4af6-b8a8-6dc3d226ba99">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-64d573b6-6104-4af6-b8a8-6dc3d226ba99">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-64d573b6-6104-4af6-b8a8-6dc3d226ba99">
                Sir J. Anderson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-64d573b6-6104-4af6-b8a8-6dc3d226ba99" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-10-19/debates/46a90bb0-097c-44af-8352-6d3109fdf97b/Personnel#contribution-64d573b6-6104-4af6-b8a8-6dc3d226ba99">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I am not accepting anything as a matter of course. I am always prepared to look into anything that may be represented as verging on the unseemly, but I really cannot undertake to concern myself as a general rule <span id="1024" class="column-number" data-column-number="1024"></span> with other sources of income that volunteers may enjoy or the financial condition of their household.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-64d573b6-6104-4af6-b8a8-6dc3d226ba99" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-10-19/debates/46a90bb0-097c-44af-8352-6d3109fdf97b/Personnel#contribution-64d573b6-6104-4af6-b8a8-6dc3d226ba99">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>







<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-aa26972d-7f9a-4b0e-904f-ea61f467f38b'>
            
<p class="">67.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
